title: Stylized Flower
description: A stylized illustration of a flower with orange petals and a green center. The flower has elongated green structures at the top and several thin, curved filaments extending from the center.

title: Cartoon Flower
description: A cartoon-style illustration of a flower with orange petals and a green center. The flower has a long green stem and appears to be stylized rather than realistic.

title: White Flower with Black Spots
description: A close-up of a white flower featuring a yellow center and distinct black spots on its petals. The flower is surrounded by green foliage and buds, set against a soft blue background.

title: Colorful Flower
description: An illustration of a flower with orange petals and a green center. The flower has a green stem and several petals arranged symmetrically around the center.

title: Pine Cone on Pine Branch
description: A close-up image of a pine cone resting on a pine branch. The pine cone is brown with a textured surface, and the branch features green needles, set against a blue background.
